{"tid":2071371,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"想買凍頂烏龍做父親節禮物","createTime":"2020-06-19T19:02:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-19T20:07:38.000Z","uid":262568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b1e4c6d25831401314bd2dfb85f9bde8b10a9100","tid":2071371,"uid":262568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T19:02:17.000Z","msg":"如題，想搵啲懶係小店但係啲嘢又令嘅舖買。因為我阿爸係幾鍾意飲，我想搵啲特別啲嘅佢未必會搵到嘅。因為我Google就好多時都係出天仁，劉裕發啲大舖，因為佢平時都會買來飲我驚佢已經試過呢啲大舖。跟住我見到半島有，但我又諗貴係咪就一定好。其實一年一次都想送好少少，所以價錢唔係第一考慮，都係想送隻好飲嘅少見嘅俾老豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"588248a1da680edee587a41cd4da7d58365d06f0","tid":2071371,"uid":12146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T19:03:06.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"43d162e694287e12763f044915b85d6e50651374","tid":2071371,"uid":259532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T19:04:56.000Z","msg":"想下去台灣網搵，有啲可以網上買"},{"pid":"bc362e9d48014d9e9dffa2fd26bc93108ef17a97","tid":2071371,"uid":262568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43d162e694287e12763f044915b85d6e50651374","tid":2071371,"uid":259532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T19:04:56.000Z","msg":"想下去台灣網搵，有啲可以網上買"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T19:11:47.000Z","msg":"我又衰拖延症唔一早搵，但又想正日送到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd9c933553418db484339e0fad3fd6b39017d280","tid":2071371,"uid":37246,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T19:29:18.000Z","msg":"冇咪送住津路烏龍先囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb0839fe072f3f5a19d3c0c749ceed89269c2c27","tid":2071371,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T20:07:38.000Z","msg":"買靚茶葉餅"}]}